{"title_page": "RLSY College Aurangabad", "text_new": "{{short description|degree college in Bihar}}\n{{Primary sources|date=April 2020}}\n{{Copy edit|for=grammar, style, spelling, and usage|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date = March 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date = March 2020}}\n{{Infobox university\n| native_name = Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav College\n| image       =\n| motto       = \n| established = {{Start date and age|1971}}\n| affiliation = [[Magadh University]]\n| principal   = Dr. Vijay Kumar Sinha\n| address     = Yamuna Nagar Road (G.T Road) \n| city        = [[Aurangabad]]\n| state       = [[Bihar]]\n| country     = [[India]]\n| postalcode  = 824101\n| coordinates = \n| website     = {{URL|http://rlsycollegeaurangabad.in/}}\n}}\n'''RLSY College, Aurangabad''' also known as '''Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav College, Aurangabad''' is a degree college in [[Aurangabad District, Bihar|Aurangabad district]] of [[Bihar]], [[India]].<ref>{{cite web|title=RLSY College|url=https://www.bhaskar.com/bihar/aurangabad/news/rlsy-college-principal39s-exit-020603-4076651.html|website=Bhaskar news|accessdate=9 March 2019}}</ref> It is a constituent College of [[Magadh University]]<ref>{{cite web|title= constituent college|url=https://magadhuniversity.ac.in/list-of-constituent-colleges/|website=Magadh university}}</ref>. The college offers [[senior secondary education]], [[undergraduate degree]]s and [[Postgraduate degree]]s in arts, science and conducts some vocational courses. The college was established in 1971 by [[Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav]]<ref>{{cite web|title=establish history|url=https://schools.org.in/aurangabad-(bihar)/10340313303/ram-lakhan-singh-yadav-college-aurangabad.html|website=school org}}</ref>. \n\n== Degrees and courses ==\nThe college offers the following degrees and courses.\n\n* Senior Secondary\n** [[Intermediate of Arts]]\n** Intermediate of Science\n** Intermediate of Commerce \n* Bachelor's degree\n** [[Bachelor of Arts]]\n** [[Bachelor of Science]]\n==Campus==\n[[File:Yadav College.png|right|250px]]\nThe college is situated on a five-acre plot of land in the south of [[Aurangabad, Bihar]] on [https://www.google.com/maps/place/Yamunanagar+Rd,+Yamuna+Nagar,+Aurangabad,+Bihar+824101,+India/@24.7398131,84.3824032,957m/data=!3m2!1e3!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x398cfc457d03f565:0x64373d94d4f12fe1!8m2!3d24.7397471!4d84.3836408?hl=en-US Yamunanagar Rd] east of the [[Adri river]].\n\n== References ==\n\n\n{{Official website|http://rlsycollegeaurangabad.in/}}\n\n{{coord missing|Bihar}}\n\n[[Category:Colleges affiliated to Magadh University]]\n[[Category:1971 establishments in India]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 1971]]\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Bihar]]\n[[Category:Bhupendra Narayan Mandal University]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|degree college in Bihar}}\n{{Primary sources|date=April 2020}}\n{{Copy edit|for=grammar, style, spelling, and usage|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date = March 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date = March 2020}}\n{{Infobox university\n| native_name = Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav College\n| image       =\n| motto       = \n| established = {{Start date and age|1971}}\n| affiliation = [[Magadh University]]\n| principal   = Dr. Vijay Kumar Sinha\n| address     = Yamuna Nagar Road (G.T Road) \n| city        = [[Aurangabad]]\n| state       = [[Bihar]]\n| country     = [[India]]\n| postalcode  = 824101\n| coordinates = \n| website     = {{URL|http://rlsycollegeaurangabad.in/}}\n}}\n'''RLSY College, Aurangabad''' also known as '''Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav College, Aurangabad''' is a degree college in [[Aurangabad District, Bihar|Aurangabad district]] of [[Bihar]], [[India]].<ref>{{cite web|title=RLSY College|url=https://www.bhaskar.com/bihar/aurangabad/news/rlsy-college-principal39s-exit-020603-4076651.html|website=Bhaskar news|accessdate=9 March 2019}}</ref> It is a constituent College of [[Magadh University]]<ref>{{cite web|title= constituent college|url=https://magadhuniversity.ac.in/list-of-constituent-colleges/|website=Magadh university}}</ref>. The college offers [[senior secondary education]], [[undergraduate degree]]s and [[Postgraduate degree]]s in arts, science and conducts some vocational courses. The college was established in 1971 by [[Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav]]<ref>{{cite web|title=establish history|url=https://schools.org.in/aurangabad-(bihar)/10340313303/ram-lakhan-singh-yadav-college-aurangabad.html|website=school org}}</ref>. \n\n== Degrees and courses ==\nThe college offers the following degrees and courses.\n\n* Senior Secondary\n** [[Intermediate of Arts]]\n** Intermediate of Science\n** Intermediate of Commerce \n* Bachelor's degree\n** [[Bachelor of Arts]]\n** [[Bachelor of Science]]\n==Campus==\n[[File:Yadav College.png|right|250px]]\nThe college is situated on a five-acre plot of land.\n\n== References ==\n\n\n{{Official website|http://rlsycollegeaurangabad.in/}}\n\n{{coord missing|Bihar}}\n\n[[Category:Colleges affiliated to Magadh University]]\n[[Category:1971 establishments in India]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 1971]]\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Bihar]]\n[[Category:Bhupendra Narayan Mandal University]]\n", "name_user": "LucasWalden", "label": "vandal", "comment": "(Added Campus location details.)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RLSY_College_Aurangabad"}
